  "title": "Construction Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for execution of project, schedule planning, implementation, site management from conception, completion, TOP and DLP stage</li>\n  <li>Able to comprehend and develop different type of drawings (architectural, structural and M&amp;E)</li>\n  <li>Provide overall direction in time setting, cost and quality standards</li>\n  <li>Creative in residential layout externally and interior</li>\n  <li>Able to liaise with various key personnel to conduct regular site visits for project progress update</li>\n  <li>Handle other ad-hoc matters assigned by office</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recognized degree in Architecture, Civil or Structural or related disciplines</li>\n  <li>Min 3 years project design &amp; management experience in Singapore</li>\n  <li>Able to handle his/her project independently</li>\n  <li>High achiever, result orientated, good team player &amp; able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Great interpersonal and management skills</li>\n  <li>Proficient in computer design (e.g. ArchiCAD / Lumion) and presentation software (e.g. Photoshop, Sketchup, Powerpoint)</li>\n  <li>Able to work on Saturdays</li>\n  <li>Able to work in fast paced environment</li>\n</ul>",
